{"tid":2365740,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"是靚午 香橙燒烤醬照燒豬仔骨背肋肉 配 甜粟米洋蔥炒著仔","createTime":"2021-01-14T04:06:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-14T09:15:50.000Z","uid":33359,"like":54,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"bea56e6690968bc46fe722218cc4c2b9af8881c4","tid":2365740,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T04:06:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wDsZcYW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwDsZcYW.jpg&h=d52f3245&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LiWnVck.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLiWnVck.jpg&h=a1b0fb8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n肉有成五大舊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講吓味道先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個醬唔係好食得出有橙味<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但甜酸味夠得黎又唔會太漏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n配埋個豬仔骨食好夾<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n豬仔骨肉質好嫩滑<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食到啲豬油脂既香氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n愈食愈爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n直接戴手套不顧儀態咁猛𡁻<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n炒著仔唔洗多講<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一樣咁好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食完成個人都c伏哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n觀塘飲食mewe谷已突破5千人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想知觀塘有乜好食快啲入<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://mewe.com/join/觀塘飲食台1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F